#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Abrahms Recipes 1"
msgstr "亚伯拉罕食谱 1"

#. ~ Description for Abrahms Recipes 1
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds some simple recipes, ingredients and meals that don't require advanced "
"tools to make. Also adds some slightly overpowered historical and mythical "
"melee weapons from Europe, China and Japan"
msgstr "添加一些无需高级工具即可制作的简单食谱、食材和餐点。同时加入一些来自欧洲、中国和日本的历史与神话近战武器，它们略微过于强大。"

#: .\items\comestibles\carnivore.json
msgid "minced meat"
msgid_plural "minced meat"
msgstr[0] "肉末"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'minced meat', 'str_pl': 'minced meat'}
#: .\items\comestibles\carnivore.json
msgid ""
"When you don't have a meat grinder, a knife or food processor will do the "
"job. A finely chopped or ground paste of assorted meat, fat, gristle, and "
"connective tissues."
msgstr "当你没有绞肉机时，一把刀或食品加工机也能胜任。这是由各种肉类、脂肪、软骨和结缔组织精细切碎或研磨而成的糊状物。"

#: .\items\comestibles\carnivore.json
msgid "minced scrap"
msgid_plural "minced scraps"
msgstr[0] "碎肉屑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'minced scrap', 'str_pl': 'minced scraps'}
#: .\items\comestibles\carnivore.json
msgid "Finely chopped or ground scraps of meat."
msgstr "精细切碎或研磨的肉屑。"

#: .\items\comestibles\carnivore.json
msgid "cooked minced meat"
msgid_plural "cooked minced meat"
msgstr[0] "熟肉末"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cooked minced meat', 'str_pl': 'cooked minced
#. meat'}
#: .\items\comestibles\carnivore.json
msgid "Cooked mixed hamburger meat."
msgstr "煮熟的混合汉堡肉。"

#: .\items\comestibles\carnivore.json
msgid "meatstick"
msgid_plural "meatsticks"
msgstr[0] "肉条"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'meatstick', 'str_pl': 'meatsticks'}
#: .\items\comestibles\carnivore.json
msgid ""
"Meat that has been ground then formed into strips or sticks and smoked or "
"dehydrated. Chewier than regular jerky but with a shorter shelf life."
msgstr "将肉研磨后制成条状或棒状，再烟熏或脱水而成。比普通肉干更有嚼劲，但保质期较短。"

#: .\items\comestibles\carnivore.json
msgid "meatball"
msgid_plural "meatballs"
msgstr[0] "肉丸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'meatball', 'str_pl': 'meatballs'}
#: .\items\comestibles\carnivore.json
msgid ""
"Minced or ground meat, and optionally filler or other ingredients, mushed "
"into a ball. It can be used as a substitute for chunks of meat, or formed "
"into smaller balls for use in sauces and soups."
msgstr "将肉末或碎肉，以及可选的填充物或其他配料，揉成球状。它可以作为肉块的替代品，也可以制成更小的丸子用于酱汁和汤中。"

#: .\items\comestibles\drink_other.json
msgid "mayonnaise gummy"
msgid_plural "mayonnaise gummies"
msgstr[0] "蛋黄酱软糖"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mayonnaise gummy', 'str_pl': 'mayonnaise
#. gummies'}
#: .\items\comestibles\drink_other.json
msgid ""
"Because of its oil content, mayonnaise can't be dried into a powder, instead"
" becoming a rubbery gummy that tastes more or less like mayonnaise, but has "
"an unpleasant texture. It can't be reconstituted into spreadable mayonnaise,"
" but it can be softened by heating with water."
msgstr ""
"由于含有油脂，蛋黄酱无法干燥成粉末，反而会变成一种橡胶状的软糖，味道大致像蛋黄酱，但口感不佳。它无法还原成可涂抹的蛋黄酱，但可以通过加水加热软化。"

#: .\items\comestibles\drink_other.json
msgid "ketchup powder"
msgid_plural "ketchup powder"
msgstr[0] "番茄酱粉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ketchup powder', 'str_pl': 'ketchup powder'}
#: .\items\comestibles\drink_other.json
msgid ""
"Dehydrated ketchup, ground into a powder. Can be used as a flavouring for "
"dry snacks, or reconstituted with water."
msgstr "脱水番茄酱，研磨成粉末。可用作干零食的调味料，或加水复原。"

